"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.1.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.1.2</span> 标题：刺棒、尖头棒（goad）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：דָּרְבָן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：darvan)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:21\">1SA 13:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:11\">ECC 12:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מַלְמַד</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：malmad)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:31\">JDG 3:31</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：κέντρον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：kentron)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:14\">ACT 26:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir38:25\">SIR 38:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc14:19\">4MA 14:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/PssSol16:4\">PSS 16:4</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0966_goad_oxen_en.jpg\" alt=\"WEB-0966_goad_oxen_en\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\"> (© Unknown - Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>刺棒是一根棒子，有时带一个金属尖头（<em>darvan</em> ），用来驱赶役畜或绵羊等。刺棒必须足够长，这样人们从站立的地方就能戳到动物，因此通常为1—2米（3—6英尺）长。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>如果拉着车辆或其他东西的牲畜不肯出力，或是走错方向，驱赶的人就可以用刺棒的尖端戳刺牲畜的臀部，疼痛会迫使牲畜更加卖力或改变方向。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>如果当地人不知道役畜，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:31\">JDG 3:31</a> 中“赶牛的棍子”可以翻译成“尖头棒”或“带金属尖头的杆子”。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:11\">ECC 12:11</a> 可以扩展翻译如下：“智慧人的话语就像牧羊人用来引导羊群的尖头棒……”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直译；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"German Common Language Version (Gute Nachricht Bibel)\">GECL</abbr> 的译文类似），或“有经验之人的言语就像激动心灵的棒子……”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"French Common Language Version (Bible en français courant)\">FRCL</abbr> 直译）。另外也可以译成，“智慧人的话语锐利而精辟……”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Dutch Common Language Version\">DUCL</abbr> 直译）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:14\">ACT 26:14</a> ：这是新约中唯一出现这个词的地方，出现在短语“用脚踢刺棒”中，意思是抗拒权柄以致自己遭受伤害或痛苦，在反抗某人或某个命令时导致自己受到伤损。这节经文的后半部分也可译成，“扫罗，你为什么逼迫我？你的反抗会让你自己受伤。”</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir38:25\">SIR 38:25</a> 中，重点是工人所做的事，因此没有必要找到一个词来翻译这件物品；例如，翻译者可以译成，“当农夫唯一的愿望就是赶牛耕地，……他怎能获得知识呢？”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直译），也可以译成，“当农夫唯一的愿望就是在牛想要停下来的时候驱赶它们继续往前走，……他怎能获得知识呢？”</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
